(6, 1, '2021-08-24 06:45:15', '2021-08-24 06:45:15', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A library management system is <strong>ERP software that is designed &amp; developed to manage all the in-house functions of a library</strong>. A librarian requires maintaining a database of new books and the books that are borrowed by users along with their due dates. This system completely automates all your library\'s activities.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<html>\n<body>\n<center>\n<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/3SDkzDlw1yc\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n</center>\n</body>\n</html>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1><a href=\"https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/986042.A_P_J_Abdul_Kalam\"><br>A.P.J. Abdul Kalam</a> </h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Showing 1-30 of 471“Dream is not that which you see while sleeping it is something that does not let you sleep.”<br>―&nbsp;<strong>A P J Abdul Kalam</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'About', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'about', '', '', '2021-08-25 09:10:48', '2021-08-25 09:10:48', '', 0, 'http://localhost/my-files/library/?page_id=6', -24, 'page', '', 0),
